STATE
v.
John David WILLIAMS. No. 235P08-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 26, 2008. Elizabeth L. McKay, Special Deputy Attorney General, Rick Shaffer, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 13th day of June 2008 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of August 2008."
